  "text": "More than 100 overlapping theories, conceptual models, and frameworks have been proposed to describe the process of implementation [CITATION_1] , classify various implementation strategies [CITATION_2] , and provide guidance when evaluating implementation efforts [CITATION_3] . A recent book describes several of these frameworks for implementation science and their implications for health care and public health [CITATION_4] .",
